'''史堤芬·柏德列·亨特'''（{{lang-en|'''Stephen Patrick Hunt'''}}，{{bd|1981年|8月1日|catIdx=Hunt, Stephen}}），出生在[[萊伊什郡|萊伊什郡]][[波力胥|波力胥]]，是一名[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]][[足球員|足球員]]，司職[[左翼|左翼]]，亦可出任[[左閘|左閘]]和[[攻擊中場|攻擊中場]]。他出身於[[水晶宮足球會|水晶宮]]青訓系統，亦曾效力[[賓福特足球會|賓福特]]、[[雷丁足球會|雷丁]]和[[侯城足球會|侯城]]。

他的弟弟{{le|路爾·亨特|Noel Hunt}}亦是一名足球員。

== 球會 ==
;早年
亨特憑著他的創造力、技術以及其作為翼鋒的效率而為人熟悉。雖然，他在[[萊伊什郡|萊伊什郡]]出世，但卻在[[沃特福德_(赫特福德郡)|沃特福德]]長大。他是一名未成年的天才[[板棍球|板棍球]]球員和足球員。他曾效力於{{Link-en|沃特福德投手|Waterford GAA}}的U15和U16組別<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
 |url          = http://www.munster-express.ie/sports/gaa-football/stephen-hunt-signs-for-club-deise/
 |title        = Stephen Hunt signs for Club Déise
 |publisher    = Munster Express
 |date         = 16 June 2008
 |accessdate   = 27 January 2009
 |archive-date = 2017-02-01
 |archive-url  = https://web.archive.org/web/20170201233852/http://www.munster-express.ie/sports/gaa-football/stephen-hunt-signs-for-club-deise/
 |dead-url     = no
}}</ref>。他首次接觸足球是他在11歲時轉去位於沃特福德的錫安山中學（Mount Sion secondary school）就讀。他在中學時期就開始代表當地足球會約翰韋利（Johnville）上陣。這使他具備一定的知名度，他亦有代表沃特福德郡迪出戰肯尼迪盃（Kennedy Cup）。他在卡里克聯（Carrick United）的各年齡層級別均表現出色，後來他前往[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]當上[[水晶宮足球會|水晶宮]]的學徒球員。由於他未能在-{一隊}-帶來衝擊，他因而前往多間球會試訓，其中包括[[登地聯足球會|登地聯]]<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.dundeeunitedfc.co.uk/index.asp?tm=3&nID=329&cd=2001&cd1=1|title=Decision Time fpr Trial Trio|date=22 January 2001|publisher=Dundee United F.C.|accessdate=23 January 2009|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120728170713/http://www.dundeeunitedfc.co.uk/index.asp?tm=3&nID=329&cd=2001&cd1=1|archivedate=2012年7月28日}}</ref>，最終加盟[[賓福特足球會|賓福特]]。他在這支倫敦西部球會效力四年，成為球隊重要的成員。
2005年，他拒絕新約並決定離開賓福特。他同意加盟[[巴拉福特足球會|巴拉福特]]後，[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]球會[[雷丁足球會|雷丁]]表示對他有興趣，使他改變了想法。

;雷丁
亨特在加盟雷丁的首個球季並不幸運，由於[[卜比·干維|卜比·干維]]的狀態較好，所以他並未能在大部分賽事正選上陣。不過，他仍然作出不錯的貢獻，從後備席入替。2005/06球季，雷丁贏得聯賽冠軍並升班至[[英格蘭足球超級聯賽|英超]]。

2006年10月14日，亨特在[[米底捷斯基球場|米底捷斯基球場]]對[[車路士足球會|車路士]]的賽事中，由於爭奪皮球而使其膝蓋撞到對方[[門將|門將]][[佩特·施治|佩特·施治]]，導致對方[[顱骨骨折|凹陷性頭骨骨折]]而需要接受手術<ref name="BBC Cech surgery">{{en}}{{cite web | date=15 October 2006 | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/chelsea/6053244.stm | title=Keeper Cech has surgery on skull | publisher=BBC | work=BBC Sport | accessdate=23 January 2009 | archive-date=2008-04-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080411054213/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/chelsea/6053244.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。意外後，英超官方、球員、學者、球員代表，甚至是[[議員|議員]]都此加以譴責<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | date=14 October 2006 | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/chelsea/6052028.stm | title=Mourinho angry as keepers injured | publisher=BBC | work=BBC Sport | accessdate=23 January 2009 | archive-date=2008-12-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081210111903/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/chelsea/6052028.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref> 或支持<ref>{{en}}{{cite news | date=14 October 2006 | url=http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~912021,00.html | title=Coppell gives his views on Chelsea game, Hunt collision, ref Riley and more | publisher=readingfc.co.uk | accessdate=23 January 2009 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120805171837/http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~912021,00.html | archivedate=2012年8月5日 }}</ref>。他和其他捲入這事件的人，最終都未有被[[英格蘭足球總會|英足總]]懲處<ref>{{en}}{{cite news | date=19 October 2006 | url=http://www.thefa.com/TheFA/Disciplinary/NewsAndFeatures/Postings/2006/10/ReadingChelsea.htm | title=Reading/Chelsea statement | publisher=thefa.com | accessdate=23 January 2009 | archive-date=2008-12-03 | archive-url=https://archive.is/20081203215708/http://www.thefa.com/TheFA/Disciplinary/NewsAndFeatures/Postings/2006/10/ReadingChelsea.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>，但與此同時，他和隊友{{Link-en|伊巴謙馬·辛高|Ibrahima Sonko}}被指在同一場賽事撞到佩特·施治的替補[[卡路·古迪仙尼|卡路·古迪仙尼]]，並據稱收到車路士球迷死亡恐嚇<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | date=16 November 2006 | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/r/reading/6153958.stm | title=Police probe Royals death threats | publisher=BBC | work=BBC Sport | accessdate=23 January 2009 | archive-date=2007-01-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070124235412/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/r/reading/6153958.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news | date=17 November 2006 | url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/article/0,,30269-2457433,00.html | title=Reading pair get death threats as Chelsea row turns sinister | publisher=The Times | accessdate=23 January 2009 | first=Russell | last=Kempson }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news | date=16 November 2006 | url=http://www.chelseafc.com/article.asp?hlid=429292&title=Statement+on+Reading+threats&nav=news | title=Statement on Reading Threats | publisher=www.chelseafc.com | accessdate=23 January 2009 | archive-date=2018-12-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216100747/https://www.chelseafc.com/article.asp?hlid=429292&title=Statement+on+Reading+threats&nav=news | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2007年7月9日，他與球會簽訂條件更好的三年合約，使他待在雷丁至2009/10球季<ref>{{en}}{{cite news | date=9 July 2007 | url=http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~1069832,00.html | title=Hunt signs new contract | work=readingfc.co.uk | accessdate=23 January 2009 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080413192104/http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~1069832,00.html | archivedate=2008年4月13日 }}</ref>。

在2008年1月轉會市場時，雷丁拒絕了[[新特蘭足球會|新特蘭]]對亨特的250萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]<ref name="BBC not selling">{{en}}{{cite web | date=31 December 2007 | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7165934.stm | title=Reading rule out Hunt departure | publisher=BBC | work=BBC Sport | accessdate=23 January 2009 | archive-date=2008-01-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080103051416/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7165934.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Times not selling">{{en}}{{cite news | date=31 December 2007 | url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/premier_league/article3113829.ece | title=Reading hoping to hang on to Stephen Hunt | publisher=The Times | accessdate=23 January 2009}}</ref>、300萬英鎊<ref>{{en}}{{cite news | date=7 January 2008 | url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11661_3029366,00.html | title=Blacks Cats fail in second bid for Royals ace | publisher=Sky Sports | accessdate=23 January 2009 | archive-date=2009-08-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090814172737/http://www.skysports.com/story/0%2C19528%2C11661_3029366%2C00.html | dead-url=no }}</ref> 和450萬英鎊<ref>{{en}}{{cite news | date=10 January 2008 | url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/pages/live/articles/sport/football.html?in_article_id=507434&in_page_id=1779 | title=Sunderland raise Hunt bid to £4.5m | work=The Daily Mail | accessdate=23 January 2009}}</ref> 和最後500萬英鎊的出價<ref>{{en}}{{cite news | date=24 January 2008 | url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/premier_league/article3241352.ece | title=Tottenham step up bid to clinch deal for Tiago | work=The Times | accessdate=23 January 2009}}</ref>，並證實他們無意在轉會市場出售球員<ref name="BBC not selling" /><ref name="Times not selling" />。2月1日，他與球會續約至2011年夏天<ref>{{en}}{{cite news | date=1 February 2008 | url=http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~1231200,00.html | title=Hunt signs a new contract | work=readingfc.co.uk | accessdate=23 January 2009 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120805162041/http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~1231200,00.html | archivedate=2012年8月5日 }}</ref>。2007/08球季，他總共上陣39次及攻入6球。

2009年2月4日，他與球會簽訂三年半合約，使他留效至2012年夏天<ref>{{en}}{{cite news | date=4 February 2009 | url=http://www.readingfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~1544403,00.html | title=Hunt to extend contract | work=readingfc.co.uk | accessdate=4 February 2009 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090207014037/http://readingfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0%2C%2C10306~1544403%2C00.html | archivedate=2009年2月7日 }}</ref>。然而，他在同年6月9日宣佈他希望離開雷丁並重返英超<ref>{{en}}{{cite news | date=9 June 2009 | url=http://msnsport.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_5370673,00.html | title=Hunt seeks 'fresh start' | work=msnsport.skysports.com | accessdate=9 June 2009 | archive-date=2009-07-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090704005553/http://msnsport.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_5370673,00.html | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

;侯城
8月13日，亨特被[[侯城足球會|侯城]]以據指350萬英鎊轉會費買入<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/hull_city/8194503.stm|title=Hull complete Hunt & Ghilas deals|date=13 August 2009|publisher=BBC|work=BBC Sport|accessdate=13 August 2009|archive-date=2018-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180216085856/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/hull_city/8194503.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月15日，他在對車路士的賽事中首次亮相28分鐘便攻入其處子入球<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8199453.stm | title=Chelsea 2 – 1 Hull | date=15 August 2009 | work=BBC Sport | publisher=BBC | accessdate=9 January 2010 | archive-date=2016-01-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160112205124/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8199453.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。這亦是[[2009年至2010年英格蘭超級聯賽|2009/10球季]]的首個入球。然而，由於佩特·施治事件，他整場賽事都遭到車路士的球迷的嘲諷。他亦在緊接以1-5的比分大敗予[[熱刺足球會|熱刺]]的賽事中於主場處子上陣並取得入球<ref>{{en}}{{cite web
