 }}</ref>。

1月轉會市場時，英超[[狼隊足球會|狼隊]]出價500萬英鎊希望買入亨特，但被侯城拒絕<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/h/hull_city/8491554.stm|title=Hull reject Wolves transfer bid for Stephen Hunt|date=1 February 2010|publisher=BBC|work=BBC Sport|accessdate=2010-03-21|archive-date=2010-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100204093636/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/h/hull_city/8491554.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2月份足傷後一直缺陣，於4月13日經探知手術後證實提前結束球季<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/hull_city/8618109.stm |title=Stephen Hunt injury hits Hull survival hopes |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-04-13 |accessdate=2010-06-22 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307122845/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/hull_city/8618109.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，而球隊亦於季後降班返回[[英冠|英冠]]。

;狼隊
