== 國際賽 ==
2007年2月7日，亨特在客場以2-1的比分擊敗[[聖馬力諾國家足球隊|聖馬力諾]]的賽事中後備入替而首次代表[[愛爾蘭國家足球隊|愛爾蘭]]上陣<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | date=7 February 2007 | title=San Marino 1-2 Rep of Ireland | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6340553.stm | publisher=BBC | work=BBC Sport | accessdate=23 January 2009 | archive-date=2007-02-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070209064000/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6340553.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref> 。3月24日，他在主場以1-0的比分擊敗[[威爾斯足球代表隊|威爾斯]]的賽事中再次以後備形式入替而第二次上陣<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | date=24 March 2007 | title=Rep of Ire 1-0 Wales | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6439991.stm | publisher=BBC | work=BBC Sport | accessdate=23 January 2009 | archive-date=2007-03-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070317181506/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6439991.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

9月12日，他亦有在以0-1的比分不敵[[捷克國家足球隊|捷克]]的賽事中後備入替，然而[[希臘|希臘]]球證{{Link-en|奇羅斯·華沙拉斯|Kyros Vassaras}}指他侵犯[[真·保勒|真·保勒]]而被趕離場，其後報告指這決定過於嚴厲，因為亨特似乎贏得皮球<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | date=12 September 2007 | title=Czech Republic 1-0 Rep of Ireland | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6992042.stm | publisher=BBC | work=BBC Sport | accessdate=23 January 2009 | archive-date=2009-04-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090416132357/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6992042.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

